arts.ttl: City's Greenwood stretchered off with knee injury
arts.sum: England and Manchester City defender Alex Greenwood was stretched off in the club's Women's Champions League win over St. Pölten on Thursday.

arts.ttl: Alex Greenwood injury overshadows Manchester City win over St Polten
arts.sum: The England international went down clutching her left knee.

arts.ttl: Watch Live: City v St Polten Open Training
arts.sum: Tune in to City's final training session ahead of our UEFA Women's Champions League clash with St Polten. However, top spot in Group D is still up for grabs with City currently in the driver’s seat ahead of reigning European champions Barcelona.
